  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE THE MISSISSIPPI JENNA'S LAW TASK FORCE; TO REQUIRE THE TASK FORCE TO STUDY THE INCLUSION OF INFORMATION ON AUTOPSIES RELATED TO SEIZURES OR EPILEPSY; TO PROVIDE FOR THE MEMBERS OF THE TASK FORCE; TO PROVIDE TIMELINES FOR THE TASK FORCE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
